---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="WiFi & Network Repair Romford - Same Day Service"
  description="WiFi and network repair in Romford. Dead spots, slow speeds, dropouts & router setup. £20 diagnostic — waived with repair. Call 07971 331814."
  keywords="wifi repair romford, network setup romford, wifi problems romford, internet not working romford, router setup romford, slow wifi romford, wifi dead spots romford, network troubleshooting romford"
  type="service"
  publishedTime="2026-03-08"
  modifiedTime="2026-03-08"
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
    { name: 'Services', url: '/services/repairs/' },
    { name: 'Network & WiFi Romford', url: '/services/network-wifi-romford/' },
  ]}
>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    html,
    body {
      overflow-x: hidden;
      width: 100%;
    }
    :root {
      --cosmic-blue: #1e3a8a;
      --nebula-purple: #7c3aed;
      --starlight-white: #f8fafc;
      --plasma-cyan: #06b6d4;
      --aurora-green: #10b981;
      --solar-orange: #f59e0b;
      --deep-space: #0f172a;
      --comet-silver: #e5e7eb;
    }
    .space-font {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .alien-font {
      font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;
    }
    .tech-font {
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    }
    @keyframes cosmic-pulse {
      0%,
      100% {
        text-shadow: 0 0 5px currentColor;
      }
      50% {
        text-shadow: 0 0 15px currentColor;
      }
    }
    @keyframes galaxy-flow {
      0% {
        background-position: 0% 0%;
      }
      50% {
        background-position: 100% 100%;
      }
      100% {
        background-position: 0% 0%;
      }
    }
    .cosmic-glow {
      animation: cosmic-pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }
    .galaxy-text {
      background: linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        var(--plasma-cyan),
        var(--aurora-green),
        var(--solar-orange)
      );
      background-size: 200% 200%;
      animation: galaxy-flow 4s ease-in-out infinite;
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    .section-bg {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.95), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9));
    }
    .cosmic-card {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9), rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.1));
      border: 1px solid var(--plasma-cyan);
      border-radius: 20px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.2);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .cosmic-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      border-color: var(--aurora-green);
    }
    .space-button {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cosmic-blue), var(--nebula-purple));
      border: 1px solid var(--aurora-green);
      color: var(--starlight-white);
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .space-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.4);
    }
    .services-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .services-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .container {
        padding: 0 16px;
      }
    }
    .area-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.3);
      border-radius: 20px;
      color: var(--comet-silver);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 13px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .area-tag:hover {
      background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.2);
      border-color: var(--plasma-cyan);
      color: var(--plasma-cyan);
    }
  </style>

  <div>
    <section class="section-bg" style="padding: 100px 0 60px;">
      <div class="container">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 50px;">
          <div
            style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.15); padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 25px; border: 1px solid var(--plasma-cyan); margin-bottom: 24px;"
          >
            <span class="tech-font" style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: 13px;"
              ><span aria-hidden="true">📡</span> WIFI & NETWORK SUPPORT</span
            >
          </div>
          <h1
            class="space-font galaxy-text cosmic-glow"
            style="font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 48px); margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.1;"
          >
            NETWORK & WIFI ROMFORD
          </h1>
          <p
            class="alien-font"
            style="font-size: clamp(16px, 3vw, 20px); color: var(--comet-silver); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 30px; line-height: 1.6;"
          >
            WiFi not working? Slow internet? Dead spots around your home? We fix WiFi and
            network issues for homes and small businesses across Romford. From router setup to
            full network troubleshooting — we'll get you connected.
          </p>
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <a href="/contact/" class="space-button space-font"><span aria-hidden="true">📡</span> Book Call-Out</a>
            <a
              href="tel:+447971331814"
              class="space-button space-font"
              style="background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);"><span aria-hidden="true">📱</span> 07971 331814</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-bg" style="padding: 60px 0;">
      <div class="container">
        <h2
          class="space-font galaxy-text cosmic-glow"
          style="font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 36px); margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: center;"
        >
          COMMON WIFI & NETWORK ISSUES
        </h2>
        <div class="services-grid">
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px; text-align: center;">
            <span style="font-size: 36px; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px;" aria-hidden="true">📵</span><h3
              class="space-font"
              style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;"
            >
              WIFI DEAD SPOTS
            </h3><p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px;">
              WiFi doesn't reach certain rooms? We optimise router placement, configure mesh
              systems, or install WiFi extenders to eliminate dead zones.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px; text-align: center;">
            <span style="font-size: 36px; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px;" aria-hidden="true">🐢</span><h3
              class="space-font"
              style="color: var(--solar-orange); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;"
            >
              SLOW SPEEDS
            </h3><p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px;">
              Not getting the speeds you're paying for? We diagnose whether it's a router issue,
              interference, or ISP problem and fix it.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px; text-align: center;">
            <span style="font-size: 36px; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px;" aria-hidden="true">🔌</span><h3
              class="space-font"
              style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;"
            >
              DROPOUTS & DISCONNECTIONS
            </h3><p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px;">
              Internet keeps dropping out? WiFi disconnecting randomly? We identify the cause —
              whether it's hardware, interference, or configuration.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px; text-align: center;">
            <span style="font-size: 36px; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px;" aria-hidden="true">⚙️</span><h3
              class="space-font"
              style="color: var(--nebula-purple); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;"
            >
              ROUTER & NETWORK SETUP
            </h3><p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px;">
              New router setup, mesh WiFi installation, network security configuration, and
              connecting all your devices properly.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-bg" style="padding: 60px 0;">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 40px;">
