              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3
                class="space-font"
                style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;"
              >
                <span aria-hidden="true">🖨️</span> DEVICE CONNECTIVITY
              </h3>
              <p
                class="alien-font"
                style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;"
              >
                Printers, smart TVs, smart home devices, and other gadgets not connecting?
                We'll get everything talking to your network.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3
                class="space-font"
                style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;"
              >
                <span aria-hidden="true">🔒</span> NETWORK SECURITY
              </h3>
              <p
                class="alien-font"
                style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;"
              >
                Secure your WiFi network with strong passwords, proper encryption, and firewall
                configuration to keep unwanted users out.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-bg" style="padding: 60px 0;">
      <div class="container">
        <h2
          class="space-font"
          style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: clamp(20px, 4vw, 28px); margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;"
