        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px;">
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3
              class="space-font"
              style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px;"
            >
              My WiFi doesn't reach upstairs — can you fix this?
            </h3>
            <p
              class="alien-font"
              style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;"
            >
              Yes! Poor WiFi coverage is very common in multi-storey homes. We can optimise your
              router placement, set up a mesh WiFi system, or install a WiFi extender to ensure
              strong coverage throughout your entire home.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3
              class="space-font"
              style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px;"
            >
              My internet keeps disconnecting — is it my router or my ISP?
            </h3>
            <p
              class="alien-font"
              style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;"
            >
              We'll diagnose whether the problem is your router, your internal wiring, WiFi
              interference, or your ISP's service. If it's an ISP issue, we'll help you
              communicate the problem to them with the evidence they need.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3
              class="space-font"
              style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px;"
            >
              Can you set up a new router for me?
            </h3>
            <p
              class="alien-font"
              style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;"
            >
              Absolutely. We set up and configure new routers, including WiFi name and password,
              security settings, port forwarding, and connecting all your devices. We can also
              recommend the best router for your home and internet plan.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3
              class="space-font"
              style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px;"
            >
              How much does WiFi troubleshooting cost?
            </h3>
            <p
              class="alien-font"
              style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;"
            >
              Our WiFi and network troubleshooting starts with a £20 diagnostic — waived if you
              proceed with the fix. Most network issues are resolved for £40-£80 depending on
              complexity. We're open 7 days, 9AM-9PM, and serve all of Romford.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

